INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES("53", "1", "2016-12-22 16:13:21", "2016-12-22 16:13:21", "<section class=\"fw-main-row  typography-special bg- \">\n    <span class=\"bg-image-overlay bg-\"></span>\n    <div class=\"fw-container-fluid unyson_fullwidth\">\n		        <div class=\"container has-container\">\n							<div class=\"row\">\n	<div class=\"col-md-12       \">\n    <div style=\"margin:;padding:\">\n	\n\n    <div class=\"fw-divider__space-30x  \"></div>\n    </div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"row\">\n	<div class=\"col-md-12       \">\n    <div style=\"margin:;padding:\">\n	<p><a href=\"http://localhost/wp/BlackOuro/pages/typography/depositphotos_49061977_original/\"><img class=\"alignleft wp-image-72\" src=\"http://localhost/wp/BlackOuro/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Depositphotos_49061977_original-1024x681.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"370\" height=\"246\" /></a>Hamburger shoulder salami jowl leberkas rump. Tenderloin boudin capicola t-bone picanha tail. Ground round cupim picanha ribeye. Shank beef ribs pork chop beef, capicola spare ribs ribeye picanha frankfurter ham pork loin andouille cow short ribs landjaeger. Tenderloin filet mignon ham pork salami.</p><p>Ground round frankfurter jerky, flank alcatra picanha beef bresaola. Meatloaf porchetta capicola andouille ground round, turducken short ribs picanha cow hamburger salami chuck fatback. Landjaeger beef bacon tri-tip doner, ball tip turducken. Filet mignon bacon bresaola ribeye.</p><p>Ball tip meatball flank kevin turducken chicken tail, shoulder beef corned beef leberkas bresaola ground round short ribs. Venison tenderloin meatloaf strip steak meatball chicken.</p>    </div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"row\">\n	<div class=\"col-md-12       \">\n    <div style=\"margin:;padding:\">\n	<p>Short ribs andouille salami beef ribs. Ham hock chicken pork loin bacon, shoulder ham pork shankle pork belly bresaola rump turkey pork chop. Jowl strip steak rump, biltong boudin tongue tail leberkas porchetta t-bone chuck s